Class
Description
App
 
Column
Annotation used to specify the mapping of a field to a column in a database table.
DtbConnexion
This class provides methods to create database connections for PostgreSQL and MySQL databases.
DtbObjectAccess
Subclass of DtbObject with additional functionality to build a primary key.
FkObject
A class representing a foreign key object used for handling database relationships.
ForeignKey
This annotation is used to mark a field as a foreign key in a database table.
Mapping
This annotation is used to specify the mapping of a class to a database table.
PrimaryKey
Indicates that a field is a primary key in a database table.
QueryBuilder
The QueryBuilder class provides methods to construct SQL queries for various database operations, such as inserting, selecting, updating, and deleting records in a database.
Utils
This class provides utility methods for the application.
View
This annotation is used to specify the view name, maximum size, order by and filters for a field in a DAO class.
XmlReader
A utility class for reading and parsing XML files.
